{"Id":826410,"Title":"南楼令·宫苑三首，叠前韵","Dynasty":"清","Author":"夏孙桐","Context":"白露冷瑶阶。停琴别有怀。旧荣华、逝水难回。自古蛾眉同见妒，邢与尹，一般哀。云雨梦荒台。谁怜宋玉才。斗新妆、争宠频来。学得楚腰人尽瘦，犹自惜，镜鸾开。花柳浮香阶。临春忆胜怀。怅西风、团扇秋回。阅尽兴亡多少事，胭井冷，几人哀。近水有楼台。题红更妙才。御沟深、一叶传来。信道宫中多秘密，鹦鹉畔，口休开。无语对空阶。长门寂寞怀。暗猜详、绿转黄回。试问倾城何结果，娃馆去，马嵬哀。桃李尽舆台。群芳未易才。顾昭阳、鸦影还来。留得凋残金粉气，生面改，待谁开。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"南楼令","Status":2,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"e0d3c567952b94002d5c56cf1f1cfd03","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":5312036,"Sentence":"留得凋残金粉气，生面改，待谁开。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"lǐu dé diāo cán jīn fěn qì ，shēng miàn gǎi ，dāi shéi kāi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":23,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5312013,"Sentence":"白露冷瑶阶。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"bái lòu lěng yáo jiē ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5312014,"Sentence":"停琴别有怀。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"tǐng qǐn bié yǒu huái ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5312017,"Sentence":"云雨梦荒台。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yún yǔ mèng huāng tāi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5312018,"Sentence":"谁怜宋玉才。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shéi lián sòng yù cái ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5312021,"Sentence":"花柳浮香阶。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"huā liu fú xiāng jiē ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":8,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5312022,"Sentence":"临春忆胜怀。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"lǐn chūn yì shēng huái ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":9,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5312025,"Sentence":"近水有楼台。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"jìn shui yǒu lóu tāi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":12,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5312026,"Sentence":"题红更妙才。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"tǐ gōng gēng miào cái ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":13,"Dynasty":"清"},{"Id":5312029,"Sentence":"无语对空阶。","Rank"